> \[!IMPORTANT\]
> This software is **Emerging** and subject to ECMWF's guidelines on [Software Maturity](https://github.com/ecmwf/codex/raw/refs/heads/main/Project%20Maturity).

**earthkit-geo** is a package for geospatial computations. It is part of the [earthkit](https://github.com/ecmwf/earthkit) ecosystem.

## Documentation

The documentation can be found at https://earthkit-geo.readthedocs.io/.

## Installation

Install via `pip` with:

```
$ pip install earthkit-geo
```

